My cell phone went dead,

01:22:18.540 --> 01:22:21.219
and I had to come in here
to find a phone to call 911.

01:22:21.300 --> 01:22:24.659
You're clever, Sue. I never
would've thought of that.

01:22:24.699 --> 01:22:27.579
Yeah, well, that's because
she's a Dundee.

01:22:29.059 --> 01:22:31.579
Or she ought to be.

01:22:31.699 --> 01:22:36.219
Uh, Jacko, keep an eye on
the goons and, uh, block your ears.

01:22:36.300 --> 01:22:39.699
- What?
