01:22:39.739 --> 01:22:42.259
No worries, mate.

01:22:43.420 --> 01:22:46.340
Uh, I have to tell you this.

01:22:47.659 --> 01:22:50.699
I was just really scared
for the first time in my life.

01:22:50.779 --> 01:22:54.259
Well, that's okay.
Most people are frightened of lions.

01:22:54.300 --> 01:22:57.179
No, not the lions.
They're just hungry.

01:22:57.219 --> 01:22:59.139
It's when I saw that goon
with a gun at your head.

01:23:00.219 --> 01:23:04.059
That's when I realized
how much I, uh--

01:23:08.139 --> 01:23:10.179
You know, um--

01:23:10.259 --> 01:23:12.579
Will you marry me?

01:23:14.340 --> 01:23:18.099
Well, you do rush into things,
don't you, Mick?

