as your wedded wife?

01:24:31.259 --> 01:24:33.579
No worries.

01:24:33.659 --> 01:24:37.579
Fair enough.
I now pronounce you...

01:24:37.659 --> 01:24:39.579
husband and wife.

01:24:39.659 --> 01:24:42.380
